Found on [[Tarsa]], enormous '''Alessian terror [[Moth/Legends|moths]]''' would swarm around any light source. [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] used the moths to scare a "city-boy" [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtrooper]] who was afraid of [[bug]]s. He frightened the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] relay base guard by turning off every light source in an area but one, which thus caused the moths to swarm.<ref name="YS">''[[Star Wars: Yoda Stories]]''</ref>

